What's his name?

20:41.921 --> 20:45.326
Garfunkel, G-O-R-F-U-N-K-E-L.

20:45.506 --> 20:48.590
That's why there's about 20 miles from around there.

20:48.930 --> 20:50.673
Yeah, you would have to meet him.

20:50.693 --> 20:51.434
He's here.

20:51.454 --> 20:52.215
Alexander.

20:53.096 --> 20:54.898
And he was in charge of rare books?

20:54.918 --> 20:57.402
Rare books in Zeitz's library.

20:57.422 --> 20:57.782
In St.

20:57.802 --> 20:58.743
Peter's library.

20:59.484 --> 21:01.207
And is he working in books here?

